athcal{A}$'s internal randomness, and may be\nof independent interest in the newly emerging area of adaptive data analysis\nwith a theoretical computer science lens.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 23 Mar 2017 16:50:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-03-24"}
