 significant improvement in QoE metrics for cloud-based video as compared\nto the considered baselines.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 24 Mar 2017 10:39:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 26 Jun 2018 11:32:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-06-27"}
