e nearly critically coupled to the ring. The demonstrated near\nunity coincidence ratio infers a near maximal heralding efficiency from the\nfabricated device. This device has the potential to greatly improve the\nscalability and performance of quantum computing and communication systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 24 Mar 2017 11:42:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-02-14"}
